If you are self-certifying your absence from an examination, please check this box. 

This box is only to be used if you have been unable to attend an examination for reasons beyond your control.  It is NOT to be used for coursework or other assessments.

By selecting this box you confirm that you have read and understood the Examination Self-Certification Policy.
